<main>
<section class="section editorial-story" id="story"><div class="wrap"><div class="section-head reveal"><p class="label">Pre-nuptial Editorial</p><div><h2>A Love That Feels Like Home</h2><p class="story-text">Quiet gestures, golden-hour laughter, and the promise that carries Marc and Jen toward August 14, 2026.</p></div></div><div class="editorial-cover reveal"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-02.jpg" alt="Marc and Jen editorial portrait"><div class="editorial-cover-copy"><p class="label">Photographed in the Philippines</p><h2>Champagne light,<br/>honest joy.</h2></div></div><div class="editorial-chapter reveal"><div class="editorial-chapter-label"><span>Chapter I</span><i></i><span>The White Series</span></div><div class="editorial-gallery"><button class="editorial-frame editorial-gallery-main" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-03.jpg" alt="Marc and Jen evening outdoor portrait"></button><div class="editorial-gallery-line"><button class="editorial-frame" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-04.jpg" alt="Marc and Jen walking by the pool"></button><button class="editorial-frame" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-05.jpg" alt="Marc and Jen rose kiss moment"></button><button class="editorial-frame" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-06.jpg" alt="Marc and Jen picnic evening session"></button></div></div></div><aside class="editorial-quote reveal"><div><span class="quote-mark">“</span><p>Two people,<br/>one story,<br/>forever unfolding.</p></div><i></i><div><span class="label">The Detail</span><p class="story-text">A ring, a promise, and the first visible sign of the life Marc and Jen are choosing together.</p></div></aside></div><div class="editorial-ring section reveal"><div class="wrap editorial-ring-inner"><div class="editorial-ring-copy"><p class="label">The Promise</p><h3>The ring. The promise. The beginning.</h3><p class="story-text">A promise held close, then shared with the world.</p></div><div class="editorial-gallery editorial-gallery-compact"><button class="editorial-frame editorial-gallery-main" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-07.jpg" alt="Jen displaying her engagement ring"></button><div class="editorial-gallery-line"><button class="editorial-frame" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-08.jpg" alt="Engagement ring detail"></button></div></div></div></div><div class="wrap"><div class="editorial-chapter reveal"><div class="editorial-chapter-label"><span>Chapter II</span><i></i><span>The Cream Series</span></div><div class="section-head"><p class="label">Featured Moments</p><h2>Light, laughter, and the quiet look of home.</h2></div><div class="editorial-gallery"><button class="editorial-frame editorial-gallery-main" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-11.jpg" alt="Marc and Jen swing moment"></button><div class="editorial-gallery-line"><button class="editorial-frame" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-09.jpg" alt="Marc and Jen on a park bench"></button><button class="editorial-frame" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-10.jpg" alt="Marc and Jen bench golden hour portrait"></button><button class="editorial-frame" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-12.jpg" alt="Marc and Jen poolside portrait"></button><button class="editorial-frame" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-13.jpg" alt="Marc and Jen park swing series"></button><button class="editorial-frame" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-14.jpg" alt="Marc and Jen tender pool moment"></button></div></div></div><div class="editorial-gallery editorial-closing-gallery reveal"><button class="editorial-panorama editorial-gallery-main" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-15.jpg" alt="Marc giving Jen a piggyback ride"><span>Joy, unscripted</span></button><div class="editorial-gallery-line"><button class="editorial-frame" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-16.jpg" alt="Prenuptial detail"></button><button class="editorial-frame" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-17.jpg" alt="Prenuptial candid"></button><button class="editorial-frame" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-18.jpg" alt="Prenuptial portrait detail"></button><button class="editorial-frame" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-19.jpg" alt="Prenuptial closing portrait"></button></div></div><p class="story-text center reveal" style="margin-top:3rem">With grateful hearts and steadfast love, Marc and Jen step into forever.</p></div></section>
<section class="section save-date-section" id="save-the-date"><div class="wrap"><div class="section-head reveal"><p class="label">Save The Date</p><div><h2>Our Save the Date</h2><p class="story-text">A glimpse of the day Marc and Jen are inviting you to remember with them.</p></div></div><div class="video-frame save-date-video reveal" data-video-src="/marc-jenny-save-the-date.mp4" data-video-poster="/images/editorial/editorial-15.jpg"><button class="video-play" type="button"><img src="/images/editorial/editorial-15.jpg" alt="Save the date poster"><span class="video-play-icon"></span><span class="video-play-text">Play Save the Date</span></button></div></div></section>
<section class="section parallax-section" id="details"><div class="wrap"><div class="arch-card reveal"><img class="crest-logo" src="/mj-wedding-logo.svg" alt="Marc and Jen monogram"><div class="center"><p class="label">With the grace of God and the blessing of our parents</p><h2 class="script-title">Marc Jherico &amp; Jenny Ruth</h2><p class="story-text" style="margin:auto">request the honor of your presence as we celebrate our love and marriage</p></div><div class="details-grid" style="margin-top:3rem"><div class="detail-block center"><p class="label">Ceremony &amp; Reception</p><h3>Friday, August 14, 2026</h3><p>3:00 in the afternoon</p><p class="story-text" style="margin:auto">Please arrive 30 minutes early</p></div><div class="rule-v"></div><div class="detail-block center"><p class="label">Venue</p><h3>Villa Juanita</h3><p>191 Look 1, Malolos, Bulacan</p><p class="story-text" style="margin:auto">Semi-formal attire requested</p></div></div><div class="btn-row"><a class="btn btn-solid" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=Villa+Juanita+191+Look+1+Malolos+Bulacan" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Get Directions</a><a class="btn" href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/render?action=TEMPLATE&amp;text=Marc+%26+Jen%27s+Wedding&amp;dates=20260814T070000Z/20260814T110000Z&amp;details=Ceremony+and+reception+at+Villa+Juanita,+191+Look+1,+Malolos,+Bulacan&amp;location=Villa+Juanita,+191+Look+1,+Malolos,+Bulacan" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Add to Calendar</a></div></div></div></section>
<section class="section" id="entourage"><div class="wrap"><div class="section-head reveal"><p class="label">With Gratitude</p><div><h2>The Entourage</h2><p class="story-text">Mirandilla · Sumilang</p></div></div><div class="arch-card reveal"><div class="role-grid"><div class="role"><span class="label">Parents of the Bride</span><p class="names">Mrs. Elenita S. Mirandilla<br>Mr. Melchor M. Mirandilla</p></div><div class="role"><span class="label">Parents of the Groom</span><p class="names">Mrs. Marian R. Sumilang<br>Mr. Enrique R. Sumilang</p></div></div><p class="sub-section-title">Officiating Minister</p><div class="role"><p class="names">Ptr. Jon Sanoy</p></div><p class="sub-section-title">Principal Sponsors</p><div class="role-grid"><div class="role"><p class="names">Dr. Rosemarie Sibbaluca Guirre<br>Mrs. Paula Cruz<br>Mrs. Marifel R. Ramirez<br>Mrs. Vilma Sumilang<br>Mrs. Mita Tan</p></div><div class="role"><p class="names">Mr. Laurence Enriquez Guirre<br>Mr. Jwilliam Cruz<br>Mr. Rodrigo Aguilar</p></div></div><div class="role-grid" style="margin-top:3rem"><div class="role"><span class="label">Maid of Honor</span><p class="names">Jazmine Sumilang</p></div><div class="role"><span class="label">Best Man</span><p class="names">Jay Micheal Cantilla</p></div></div><p class="sub-section-title">Secondary Sponsors</p><div class="role-grid wide"><div class="role"><span class="label">Veil</span><p class="names">Praise Joy S. Mirandilla<br>Jefferson R. Sumilang</p></div><div class="role"><span class="label">Jar</span><p class="names">Aivie R. Ramirez<br>Mandy Villcastin</p></div><div class="role"><span class="label">Cord</span><p class="names">Patricia Mari C. Santos<br>Christian S. Mirandilla</p></div></div><div class="role-grid" style="margin-top:3rem"><div class="role"><span class="label">Bridesmaids</span><p class="names">Praise Joy S. Mirandilla<br>Patricia Mari C. Santos<br>Annabelle C. Dilag<br>Acelyn DP. Asiddao<br>Rachel Joy U. Santos<br>Aivie R. Ramirez</p></div><div class="role"><span class="label">Groomsmen</span><p class="names">Jefferson R. Sumilang<br>Christian S. Mirandilla<br>Ryan Pascual<br>Mandy Villcastin<br>Yuan Lopez<br>Jay Cruz</p></div></div><div class="role-grid wide" style="margin-top:3rem"><div class="role"><span class="label">Coin Bearer</span><p class="names">Aivan Ramirez</p></div><div class="role"><span class="label">Bible Bearer</span><p class="names">Raymund Ivan Lopez</p></div><div class="role"><span class="label">Ring Bearer</span><p class="names">Mark Emmanuel Mirandilla</p></div></div><p class="sub-section-title">Flower Girls</p><div class="role"><p class="names">Zipporah Prail Mirandilla · Marzella Ishie Mirandilla<br>Martha Rodriguez · Bertha Rodriguez</p></div></div></div></section>
<section class="section" id="attire"><div class="wrap"><div class="section-head reveal"><p class="label">A Few Notes</p><h2>Finer Details</h2></div><div class="arch-card reveal"><div class="finer-grid"><div><p class="label">Attire Guide</p><h3>Semi-Formal Attire</h3><p class="story-text">We'd love to see you dressed in the colors of our wedding theme.</p><div class="swatches"><span class="swatch" style="background:#F3EBDD"></span><span class="swatch" style="background:#E1CBA6"></span><span class="swatch" style="background:#C9A063"></span><span class="swatch" style="background:#9C8275"></span></div></div><div><p class="label">Gift Guide</p><h3>With Love, No Boxes</h3><p class="story-text">Blessed by the Lord and by your love, your prayers are the greatest gift of all. If you wish to help us begin our new life together, a monetary gift or a surprise of your own choosing would mean the world.</p></div></div><p class="label center" style="display:block;margin-top:3rem">Reminders</p><div class="reminders"><div class="reminder"><svg width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg><span>Be On Time</span></div><div class="reminder"><svg width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 21s-7-4.6-9.3-9A5.4 5.4 0 0 1 12 6a5.4 5.4 0 0 1 9.3 6c-2.3 4.4-9.3 9-9.3 9Z"/></svg><span>Have Fun</span></div><div class="reminder"><svg width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg><span>Stay Till The End</span></div></div></div></div></section>
